                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "In order to train and compare the different algorithms, the following two datasets are used. This allows to increase the overall amount of available data and provides additional insights into how well the models can adapt to various beehives. Having a larger dataset also has another advantage because it helps prevent the issue of overfitting while training complex machine learning models."
