                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "2) Dataset 2: This dataset was created as part of the work in [29]. The data made available in [24] is a selection of recordings acquired through the NU-Hive project [30] whose main objective is to develop a beehive monitoring system capable of identifying and predict certain events and states of the hive that are of interest to the beekeeper. The dataset consists of recordings from two hives, captured in two distinct states: a \"Queen Missing\" hive, where the queen bee is absent, and a \"Normal\" hive, where no abnormal activities are observed. Each hive has a recording for each state, with each audio clip"
